<italic>p</italic>&#x02009;&#x0003e;&#x02009;0.34 vs. placebo for all comparisons</p></table-wrap-foot></table-wrap>
</p><p>
<italic>Post-hoc</italic> analysis showed that in non atopic subjects, subjects with lower baseline ACT scores (&#x02264;21), higher serum IgE (&#x0003e;200&#x000a0;IU/ml), or lower FEV1% (&#x0003c;60%), montelukast did not have a significant effect vs. placebo (Table&#x000a0;<xref rid="Tab5" ref-type="table">5</xref>).<table-wrap id="Tab5"><label>Table 5</label><caption><p>Effect of montelukast in different subjects&#x02019; subgroups</p></caption><table frame="hsides" rules="groups"><thead><tr><th/><th>Baseline</th><th>4&#x000a0;weeks</th><th>8&#x000a0;weeks</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>ACT nonatopic (montelukast)</td><td>22.2&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;1.8</td><td>20.8&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;4.6</td><td char="&#x000b1;" align="char">23.6&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;2.1</td></tr><tr><td>ACT nonatopic (placebo)</td><td/><td>23.8&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;0.8</td><td char="&#x000b1;" align="char">20.4&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;6</td></tr><tr><td>ACT&#x02009;&#x02264;&#x02009;21 (montelukast)</td><td>20.2&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;1.8</td><td>22&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;2</td><td char="&#x000b1;" align="char">21.2&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;6.4</td></tr><tr><td>ACT&#x02009;&#x02264;&#x02009;21 (placebo)</td><td/><td>21.8&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;3.3</td><td char="&#x000b1;" align="char">19.8&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;7.1</td></tr><tr><td>ACT IgE&#x02009;&#x0003e;&#x02009;200&#x000a0;IU/ml (montelukast)</td><td>22.6&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;2.7</td><td>23.5&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;1.7</td><td char="&#x000b1;" align="char">22&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;5</td></tr><tr><td>ACT IgE&#x02009;&#x0003e;&#x02009;200&#x000a0;IU/ml (placebo)</td><td/><td>23&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;3</td><td char="&#x000b1;" align="char">22&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;5.4</td></tr><tr><td>FEV1%&#x02009;&#x0003c;&#x02009;60% (montelukast)</td><td>54.5&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;5.4</td><td>50.8&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;9.5</td><td char="&#x000b1;" align="char">52.2&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;6.3</td></tr><tr><td>FEV1%&#x02009;&#x0003c;&#x02009;60% (placebo)</td><td/><td>50.3&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;4.9</td><td char="&#x000b1;" align="char">51.8&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;6.4</td></tr><tr><td>Eosinophils&#x02009;&#x02265;&#x02009;0.6&#x000a0;K/&#x003bc;L (montelukast)</td><td>0.83&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;0.22</td><td/><td char="&#x000b1;" align="char">0.54&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;0.11</td></tr><tr><td>Eosinophils&#x02009;&#x02265;&#x02009;0.6&#x000a0;K/&#x003bc;L (placebo)</td><td/><td/><td char="&#x000b1;" align="char">1.22&#x02009;&#x000b1;&#x02009;0.5</td></tr></tbody></table><table-wrap-foot><p>
